Battera::

She walked into the base and looked at the other bots standing 
around. She coughed to try to politely get some attention. "I know I 
am a new comer here. So please forgive me for trespassing on your 
terriroty. If there is no further assistance that you require from 
me, then I shall take my leave. I do not wish intrude into matters 
that you may not wish me to be apart of." Her flat black body, tall 
with her bat wings wrapped around her shoulders like a cape. She 
stood there, hoping these bots whom she had helped were going to be 
ok.
